                <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Merc</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> Dubnocaratiaco Messa Marulli </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Patera; im Zentrum eine Rosette. Z. 1 verläuft entlang des Randes; die vier Buchstaben der Z. 2 /3 befinden sich zwischen Rand und Rosette.</p>
